18 SECTION 1. NEW LAW A new section of law not to be
19 codified in the Oklahoma Statutes reads as follows:
20 This act shall be known and may be cited as the "Advancing
21 Rights for Caregiving, Health, and Extended Recovery (Maternity
22 Leave Protection for Teachers) Act" or the ARCHER Act.
